    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Foundation and in the upper right corner there is typed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the following \"MISSOURI FILTER CENTER, Robert T. Stone,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Director, 10717 E. 27th Ter., Independence, Missouri.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Below this in pencil is a notation made by Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "which is \"Air Defense Identification Zoning.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "The letter is as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "\"Dear Editor:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "\"The enclosed notice is self-explanatory. We would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "like to request this public service in the name of Truth,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "which the newspapers of our great countries so proudly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "defend and uphold.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "\"As a civilian body of investigators, we hope to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "unravel the snarled mess that shrouds the U.F.O. ques-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "tion, and with the help of the newspapers and the public,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "where can we fail?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "\"We will be grateful if you will publish the enclosed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "appeal on the front page of your newspaper, in a conspicuou",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "enough manner that no one will fail to notice it. It is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "the public we must depend upon to get thoroughly organized,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "and with this co-operation we are certain that we can find",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "the answer to the riddle of the \"Flying Saucers.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "\"If a filter center has been established in your",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "state or province, this form letter will carry its",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "address which should replace the Headquarters address",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "given on the enclosed \"Public Notice.\" If no such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
